                  <p class='text-text-inverse font-medium text-[18px] text-center'>
                    Print your own design
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <img
                src='{{ 'whole-sale-img-2.png' | asset_url }}'
                alt='Wholesale info'
                class='w-full h-full object-cover rounded-[16px]'
                width='100%'
                height='100%'>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-[24px]'>
            <p class='text-text-primary text-[18px] font-medium'>
              We are proud to offer you an innovative and sustainable solution for your golf business. Our                            
                            biodegradable balls are made from materials that easily decompose in water, meaning they
                            leave no unwanted waste in the environment.
            </p>
            <p class='text-text-primary text-[18px] font-medium'>
              This eco-friendly approach not only helps protect the environment but also brings many                            
                            benefits to your business. The balls are of high quality and deliver excellent performance
                            during play. Through our wholesale offer, you can acquire these balls in larger quantities
                            at competitive prices. Additionally, as a wholesale customer, you will have access to our
                            outstanding customer service and flexible ordering options. Join us in supporting
                            sustainability in the golf industry while gaining advantages for your wholesale business.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <form class='w-full bg-surface-secondary flex flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-[16px] py-[32px] px-[24px] lg:px-[80px] md:py-[80px] gap-[32px] h-fit'>
        <p class='text-text-primary text-[24px] font-bold uppercase'>WHOLESALE INQUIRY</p>

        <div class='flex flex-col w-full gap-[16px]'>
          <input
            type='text'
            name='name'
            placeholder='Name'
            class='py-[6px] h-[48px] px-[16px] rounded-[8px] bg-surface-primary border-tertiary border-[1px] outline-none shadow-none w-full'>
          <input
            type='text'
            name='company'
            placeholder='Company'
            class='py-[6px] h-[48px] px-[16px] rounded-[8px] bg-surface-primary border-tertiary border-[1px] outline-none shadow-none w-full'>
          <input
